    "summary": [
      "The Paris Agreement, adopted in 2015 to limit global warming to 1.5°C, faces a challenging reality ten years later, with 2024 global temperatures dangerously close to the 1.5°C threshold according to the IPCC's Sixth Assessment Report.",
